# Agent Update Writing Rule

- Agar Cursor ka koi bhi agent code mein `update`, `fix`, ya `change` kare, to us change ka short written note dena mandatory hai.
- Yeh note hamesha project root ki file `AGENT_CHANGES.md` mein likha jayega (append mode).
- Note mein minimum ye 3 cheezein honi chahiye:
  1. kya change kiya
  2. kis file/path mein kiya
  3. kyu kiya (reason)
- Agar multiple files change hui ho, to har file ka alag bullet mention karo.
- Har entry ke saath date/time aur short task title likho.
- Kaam khatam karte waqt verify karo ki `AGENT_CHANGES.md` update ho chuki hai; bina is note ke task complete mat mark karo.
